OL,3,CTwo men jailed over 'brutal and
OL,4,Cunnecessary' attack that killed man
OL,6,FTwo men who kicked and punched a 50-
OL,7,Fyear-old father to death in a "brutal
OL,8,Fand unnecessary" attack outside a pub
OL,9,Fhave been jailed.
OL,11,FCowin Fuoco-Fisher and James Caswell
OL,12,Fattacked Stefan Shotton in the early
OL,13,Fhours of 28 May 2023.
OL,15,FMr Shotton, who was described as a
OL,16,F"great character", was left with
OL,17,F"catastrophic injuries" and died in
OL,18,Fhospital nine days later, police said.
