OL,6,FFuoco-Fisher, aged 26, and Caswell,
OL,7,F29, denied joint-enterprise murder but
OL,8,FFuoco-Fisher was found guilty of
OL,9,Fmurder by a jury following a three-
OL,10,Fweek trial.
OL,12,FFuoco-Fisher, of Stuart Road, was
OL,13,Fjailed for life to serve a minimum of
OL,14,F16 years when he appeared at Plymouth
OL,15,FCrown Court on Friday 19 April.
OL,17,FCaswell was found not guilty of murder
OL,18,Fbut guilty of manslaughter and was
OL,19,Fsentenced to eight years.
