OL,6,FThe court heard the fatal assault in
OL,7,FDevonport Road stemmed from an
OL,8,Fincident that began on the evening of
OL,9,F27 May 2023.
OL,11,FAll involved had separately been out
OL,12,Fdrinking in Stoke Village pubs.
OL,14,FThe jury was told Fuoco-Fisher had
OL,15,Fchallenged Mr Shotton as he believed
OL,16,Fhis behaviour towards a woman had been
OL,17,Finappropriate.
