OL,3,CTwo men jailed over 'brutal and
OL,4,Cunnecessary' attack that killed man
OL,6,FFuoco-Fisher was subsequently removed
OL,7,Ffrom the Masonic Inn after punching Mr
OL,8,FShotton in the face in the pub's
OL,9,Fsmoking area.
OL,11,FWhen Mr Shotton later became involved
OL,12,Fin an altercation outside the Stoke
OL,13,FInn, Fuoco-Fisher crossed the road and
OL,14,Fassaulted him again.
OL,16,FHe repeatedly punched the victim and
OL,17,Fkicked him once he had fallen to the
OL,18,Ffloor.
OL,20,FCaswell was also seen punching and
OL,21,Fkicking Mr Shotton.
