OL,6,FThe victim was able to talk about the
OL,7,Fassault ` naming Fuoco-Fisher to
OL,8,Fpolice at the scene ` and was taken to
OL,9,Fhospital by officers.
OL,11,FBut his condition then deteriorated,
OL,12,Fand scans revealed he had suffered a
OL,13,Fmassive bleed on the brain.
OL,15,FMr Shotton underwent major surgery in
OL,16,Fa bid to save his life and was placed
OL,17,Finto an induced coma, but he died on 6
OL,18,FJune 2023.
