OL,6,FBoth defendants were initially
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of causing
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent.
OL,10,FThey were charged with joint-
OL,11,Fenterprise murder following Mr
OL,12,FShotton's death.
OL,14,FFuoco-Fisher admitted punching Mr
OL,15,FShotton but that it was not with
OL,16,Fenough force to cause serious injury.
OL,18,FHe told detectives Caswell had kneed
OL,19,Fthe victim and said to him he had
OL,20,F"split his head right open".
