OL,6,FThe family statement said: "We are
OL,7,Fdeeply saddened by the events of that
OL,8,Fnight and after viewing the CCTV and
OL,9,Fbodycam footage we remain shocked
OL,10,Fabout the behaviour of several key
OL,11,Findividuals.
OL,13,F"However, we would like to thank the
OL,14,Fpolice and Crown Prosecution Service
OL,15,Ffor their diligence in the criminal
OL,16,Fproceedings and those witnesses who
OL,17,Fcame forward and told the truth in
OL,18,Fcourt.
