OL,6,F"We would also like to specifically
OL,7,Fthank the ICU at Derriford for their
OL,8,Fkindness and best efforts with our
OL,9,Ffather. He will be missed."
OL,11,FSenior Investigating Officer Detective
OL,12,FInspector Rob Smith, of the Major
OL,13,FCrime Investigation Team, said: "It
OL,14,Fwas a brutal and unnecessary attack on
OL,15,FStefan Shotton.
OL,17,F"Stefan has been described as a great
OL,18,Fcharacter who loved his kids and the
OL,19,Fpeople around him very much.
