OL,6,F"This senseless attack has not only
OL,7,Fresulted in the tragic death of Stefan
OL,8,Fbut has caused absolute devastation to
OL,9,Fthe lives of his close friends and
OL,10,Ffamily.
OL,12,F"I would like to pay tribute to
OL,13,FStefan's family who have shown great
OL,14,Fstrength throughout the trial process,
OL,15,Fand I thank them for the support they
OL,16,Fhave given to the police.
